\b 5. What is SEO (Search Engine Optimization), and how can web developers optimize their websites for better search engine rankings?\par
Ans: \b0 Search Engine Optimization (SEO) is the process of optimizing a website to rank higher in search engine results pages (SERPs) for relevant keywords and phrases. SEO helps increase organic (non-paid) traffic to a website, resulting in more visibility, leads, and conversions.\par
Web developers can optimize their websites for better search engine rankings by following some best practices such as:\par

