{\pntext\f0 5.\tab}\b Building high-quality backlinks:\b0  Earn links from other authoritative and relevant websites to increase the authority and credibility of your website.\par
{\pntext\f0 6.\tab}\b Making the website mobile-friendly:\b0  Optimize your website for mobile devices as more and more users are accessing the web from their mobile phones.\par
{\pntext\f0 7.\tab}\b Using structured data:\b0  Implement structured data markup to help search engines understand the content of your website and display rich snippets in SERPs.\par

